00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:01,000
[SPEAKER_12] It has no root.

536
00:52:01,000 --> 00:52:19,000
[SPEAKER_12] We're being called as entrepreneurs instead to plant our seeds in good soil, where it might grow slower and more organically at the beginning, but ultimately it will produce a crop a hundred or 60 or 30 times what was sown.

537
00:52:19,000 --> 00:52:29,000
[SPEAKER_12] And that is the beauty with organic growth, with bootstrapping, with starting small, growing organically from customer revenue.

