00:54:37,000 --> 00:54:39,000
[SPEAKER_12] What about sabbaticals, right?

559
00:54:39,000 --> 00:54:44,000
[SPEAKER_12] And understanding that we too need this and that this nourishes our soul.

560
00:54:44,000 --> 00:54:49,000
[SPEAKER_12] And we need this as entrepreneurs to be creative and to create.

561
00:54:49,000 --> 00:54:56,000
[SPEAKER_12] The fifth discipline of contemplative entrepreneurship is silence and prayer.

562
00:54:56,000 --> 00:55:08,000
[SPEAKER_12] And it's very easy for us entrepreneurs to be hyperactive and to constantly, again, fill up all of our time with meetings and with activities and with sales calls and with.

563
00:55:08,000 --> 00:55:19,000
[SPEAKER_12] But we also need to understand that we need to create space and we need to create silence for the discerning, right?

564
00:55:19,000 --> 00:55:27,000
[SPEAKER_12] So we can actually step back occasionally and really be able to reflect in silence.

565
00:55:27,000 --> 00:55:31,000
[SPEAKER_12] It could be just taking some time to do some journaling.

566
00:55:31,000 --> 00:55:35,000
[SPEAKER_12] It could be going to the church and taking some time to pray.

567
00:55:35,000 --> 00:55:40,000
